# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]


## [1.2.0] - 2024-05-07

### Added

- Game engine rewritten as more of a state machine
- Rewrite allowed introduction of "board clearing" state
    - 500 ms freeze to the game
    - Completed lines now flash before being removed

### Fixed

- When game is launched a "press any key to start" message is displayed rather than having the game start immediately


## [1.1.1] - 2024-05-05

### Changed

- Minor optimization:  checks for completed rows are now confined to rows covered by the placed tetromino, not the entire board
- Additional stats added to high scores file
    - Number of lines completed of each type
    - Number of tetrominos of each type placed


## [1.1.0] - 2024-04-29

### Added

- External high scores file
- High score retention/display

### Fixed

- Terminal sizing communicated on error now reflects actual size requirements


## [1.0.0] - 2024-04-26

### Added

- Initial release
